<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ExamEase</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #343a40;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('header.ejs') %>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to ExamEase</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>About ExamEase</h2>

        <p>Welcome to ExamEase, your ultimate destination for seamless exam preparation! At ExamEase, we are
            dedicated to revolutionizing the way students prepare for their exams, making learning more accessible,
            engaging, and effective than ever before.</p>

        <p>Our platform offers a wide range of features and resources to help you ace your exams:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access to a vast library of study materials, including notes, videos, and practice tests</li>
            <li>Interactive learning tools and quizzes to test your knowledge and track your progress</li>
            <li>Expertly curated content tailored to your specific exam requirements</li>
            <li>Collaborative study groups and forums to connect with fellow students and share insights</li>
            <li>Personalized study plans and recommendations based on your learning goals</li>
        </ul>

        <p>With ExamEase, you can study smarter, not harder, and approach your exams with confidence. Join us today
            and take the first step towards academic success!</p>
    </div>

    <%- include('footerProfile.ejs') %>
</body>

</html>
